#. (itstool) path: page/p
#: C/beginning.page:39
msgid ""
"You can also <link xref=\"15-Puzzle#15-keyboard\">play with the keyboard</"
"link> if you prefer."
msgstr ""
"Егер қаласаңыз, <link xref=\"15-Puzzle#15-keyboard\">пернетақтамен де "
